qx|DU5, Ducking in Desperation|
HT|E|CS|1|CP|4|AT|^-{    DUCKING IN DESPERATION    }
^-|CS||CP||HT|f|AT|^B@2^Y@3The following suit distribution illustrates a ducking play which will work only about once in a half-dozen tries. Yet it may be the only possible play in hands where desperate measures are the only ones available:
|HT|i|AT|^c@D A Q 8 6 3
 

|HT|k|AT|^c@D 4 2
|
